== Page should be called "Months and Days" ==
In English, "weekday" refers only to Monday through Friday, as distinguished from "weekend", meaning Saturday and Sunday. To include all seven days, the title should be "Months and Days". I have already changed the internal reference from "weekdays" to "days of the week". [[User:Jdcrutch|Jdcrutch]] ([[User talk:Jdcrutch|discuss]] â€¢ [[Special:Contributions/Jdcrutch|contribs]]) 17:32, 9 March 2014 (UTC)

